
Integrate Gambit with Termite
=============================
1. Add a symbolic link:
  ~~lib/termite -> ..TERMITE/lib
2. Add `(include "~~lib/termite/termite.scm")` to gambit/lib/termite/termite.scm
3. Recompile and install gambit.

This is based on this article http://scheme2006.cs.uchicago.edu/09-germain.pdf written by
Guillaume Germain.
